Package Storage.Report

Class Report

java.lang.Object
Storage.Report.Report
All Implemented Interfaces:
JSONSerializable, Comparable<Report>
public class Report extends Object implements Comparable<Report>, JSONSerializable
La classe crea degli oggetti Report e permette di creare nuovi Report salvandoli nella cartella apposita di Tomcat.
